<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Activation code from web-lms</title>
    <style type="text/css">
      /* base style */
      body {
        margin: 0%;
        padding: 0%;
        min-width: 100%;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        background-color: #fafafa;
        color: #222222;
      }
      a {
        color: #000;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.25;
        text-align: center;
      }
      h2 {
        text-align: center;
      }
      p {
        margin-top: 0%;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }
      /* layout  */
      .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0% auto;
      }
      .email-header {
        background-color: #2b86ef;
        padding: 24px;
        border-top-right-radius: 4px;
        border-top-left-radius: 4px;
        color: #fff;
      }
      .email-body {
        padding: 24px;
        background-color: #fff;
      }
      .email-footer {
        background-color: #eae8e8;
        padding: 24px;
        border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;
        border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;
      }
      /* buttons  */
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #0070f3;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-align: center;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <div class="email-header">
        <h1>Welcome to web-lms</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="email-body">
        <p>Hello <%= user.name %>,</p>
        <p>
          Thank you for your registration on web-lms. To activate your account,
          please user the following activation code:
        </p>
        <h2><%=activationCode%></h2>
        <p>
          Please enter this code on the activation page within the next 5
          minutes.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you did not register for a web-lms account, please ignore this
          email.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="email-footer">
        <p>
          If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to connect us at
          <a href="mailto:rakibulhasanbu@gmail.com">rakibulhasanbu@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
